snippet.title: RACING BROS - Official trailer for Playstation 4
snippet.description:
Gather your friends and get ready for a goofy and fun
4 player racing experience for almost all ages!

Now available on Playstation Store for free

Song: Slip and Slide by Pete Masitti & John Andrew Barrow
Full game song license for Racing Bros through AudioNetwork.
